	<h1 class="title">不止中国，到处都是跌跌跌，全球股票市场怎么了？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Neil Irwin</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-25 17:12:42 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13972/medium/13972.jpg?1440495884" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13972" data-title="《不止中国，到处都是跌跌跌，全球股票市场怎么了？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13972/medium/13972.jpg?1440495884" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13972.html?source=kuhua" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
